Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:34.96,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)\pos(593,563)}Third, Farewell Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarutobi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me pull this sword out of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:01:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You ended your life in an honorable way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from someone who mastered the way of the ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My arms... feels like they're burning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission will end here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Release the field, we're going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The field...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Hokage-sama doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.21,TLnote,,0,0,0,,(Ninpou Kumoshibari: Spider Entanglement)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninpou Kumoshibari!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sticky threads that have chakra flowing through them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi! They're making a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.11,0:02:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we go after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Wait, Gai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If you make a move without knowing what happened up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.02,0:03:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you could fall into the enemy's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether there is a trap or not, we cannot let the enemy escape so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what Konoha ninjas are supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are you just going to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kabuto?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to run away from me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I show you my moves, you will just end up copying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again, it seems like you cannot use that eye perfectly like the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.76,0:03:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Temari...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kankuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... is he so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My existence will not disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It will not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you not to talk to him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's go.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There he is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monster!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Monster! Die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't get near him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't look at him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am only a relic of the past they want to get rid of.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So why do I exist and live?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And at the time, I thought of myself as...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I "had" to think of myself as...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I realized that that was the hardest thing one can feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The feeling that you are not \Nneeded by anyone in this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't get near me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain of being alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is completely out if this world, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why... but I understand your feelings so much, it actually hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... I have people who are important to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:08:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you hurt the people I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stop you, even if I have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can you do this for strangers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My loneliness... That hell, they saved me from it, and they acknowledged my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They're important to me... That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.10,0:08:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love is the spirit of devoting yourself to someone important and close to you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is expressed by caring for and protecting that person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Love...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why he's strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stop now, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be out of chakra too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the sand holding Sakura has released her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen Gaara in such a weakened state before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uzumaki Naruto, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, will I be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Temari, Kankuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is also crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The funeral for the Third Hokage, who list his life in this battle....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.51,0:12:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,as well as the other victims who gave their lives, will begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We were only able to watch, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.92,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did old man Hokage have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.31,0:13:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been a year.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It is not easy to hide your sadness and laugh, is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have heard from your teacher that you are always at the center of the laughter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's an honor for a ninja to die during a mission!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dad and mom protected this village from the monster fox with their lives...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're heroes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm the child of those heroes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sad even if I'm alone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.57,0:14:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These tears are tears of joy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can stop now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that you always hugged your knees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you are not alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All the ninjas in the Hidden Village of Konoha have a will of fire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A will of fire?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The strong will to protect Konoha.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as they have that will of fire, everyone in this village is family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Iruka, do you have it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that for Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.12,0:15:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third's funeral has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi-senpai, did you come here for Obito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've come here earlier instead of thinking up excuses for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I do... early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I come here, I feel like punishing my old foolish self.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,"A ninja must not show his emotions in any situation."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"A ninja must prioritize his mission first and must not show any tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Iruka-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do people risk their lives for others?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When one person dies... he disappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Along with his past, current lifestyle, and his future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people die in missions and wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.33,0:18:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They die easily and in surprisingly simple ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate was one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.60,0:18:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who die have goals and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But everyone has something as important as those.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Parents, siblings, friends, lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They trust and help each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.69,0:18:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The bond between the people important to you ever since birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the string that binds them becomes thicker and stronger as time goes by.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.53,0:18:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bound to you by that string will do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's important...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I think I understand, somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.42,0:19:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's painful when someone dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third didn't die for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He left something important for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find out what eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think I understand that too, somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Iruka-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the small leaves in the Hidden Village of Konoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:20:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,have inherited that will of fire you spoke of, Third.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The fire on the leaves will eventually burn greater and stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It will flash its light and protect this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,After becoming the new Hokage, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They were able to avoid complete destruction, but it looks like the damage was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The village that prospered like no other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,has become pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.22,0:20:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's out of character.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.20,0:20:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So even a person like you has an attachment to his home village?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Comment: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:05.22,ED5,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:14.49,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A cycle of hardship, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:19.76,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Inside, we were crying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:28.70,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But the one thing we won't give up\Nis the dream we've chosen, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:33.60,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's a secondary role,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:37.04,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a role in the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:42.14,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But in reaching for that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:47.92,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}let us stay centered,\Nlet us stay true
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:52.69,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Over and over,\Nwe hung on without giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.69,0:21:57.73,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Over and over,\Nwe kept coming back up
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:22:07.41,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Over and over,\Nwe believed and dreamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:13.36,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Over and over,\Nwe've seen fools
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.36,0:22:19.85,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Over and over,\Nwe've stood in the shadows of others
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:32.81,ED5,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,2000)\blur3}Now, it's our turn...\NLet us bask in our dreams
Comment: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:35.24,ED5,,0,0,0,,ED End
